Typical McDonald's.
I like this location because it is an easy to get just off the strip location.
It is perfect for a quick inexpensive breakfast.
Drive-thru is on pair with most "quick drive-thru's".
Interior is Harley-Davidson themed for those that like to look at things while they wait for food.

Sad to say, I have seen worse.
It's convenient and relatively fast.
Just not clean as it could be.
The staff here are almost as depressed as the homeless people you find hanging around it

